msgid "This notebook demostrates how to use Qiskitâ€™s implementation of the Variational Quantum Time Evolution (VarQTE) algorithm for computing the time evolving state under a given Hamiltonian. Specifically, it introduces variational quantum imaginary and real time evolution based on McLachlan's variational principle, and shows how this can be leveraged using the ``algorithms.time_evolvers.variational`` sub-module."
